high_descs: Open the fridge and remove the tomato from the shelf.
Carry the tomato to the microwave, which is to your left.
Place the tomato in the microwave and then remove once heated.
Carry the heated tomato back to the fridge.
Place the tomato on the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left head to the fridge
Open the fridge pick up the tomato then close the fridge
Turn left then head to the microwave on your right
Open the microwave then put in the tomato then close it
Turn right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge and put in tomato
anns.task_desc: Put the heated tomato on the fridge

high_descs: Turn left to face the fridge.
Take the tomato out of the fridge.
Turn left to walk to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and heat it up, removing it again.
Turn right to walk towards the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Heat a tomato up from the fridge in the microwave, putting it back in the fridge.
